title: Will Smith (rugby league)
summary:
Will Smith (born 3 July 1992) is an Australian professional rugby league footballer who plays as a five-eighth, fullback and hooker for Wests Tigers in the National Rugby League.
He previously played for the Gold Coast Titans, Parramatta Eels and the Penrith Panthers in the NRL, Hull FC in the English Super League and the Indigenous All Stars.
